WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.866
Mr. Wei, we are in trouble. What trouble?

2
00:00:03.700 --> 00:00:05.700
What are you doing here with a water hyacinth?

3
00:00:05.766 --> 00:00:07.166
Master Wei, hurry up and collect the money

4
00:00:07.166 --> 00:00:10.700
Let go of the old bug, there are different men and women, okay?

5
00:00:10.700 --> 00:00:12.466
Mei Ye, you know this thing

6
00:00:12.466 --> 00:00:15.266
Isn't this a water hyacinth? This is really a water hyacinth.

7
00:00:15.266 --> 00:00:17.533
Are you sure it's air-dried water hyacinth?

8
00:00:17.533 --> 00:00:19.366
I used to see this when I was a kid

9
00:00:19.366 --> 00:00:21.066
In the lake where I come from

10
00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:25.066
Zhou Jianzhong wants to say a few words to you alone

11
00:00:27.666 --> 00:00:29.266
Thank you Geng Chen

12
00:00:29.266 --> 00:00:30.166
I said everything

13
00:00:30.166 --> 00:00:31.566
My heart is at peace

14
00:00:31.566 --> 00:00:32.466
I'm ready

15
00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:35.066
Turn yourself in after you find Bailing River

16
00:00:35.066 --> 00:00:37.033
I've been calling you enough during this time

17
00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:38.066
Can't remember

18
00:00:38.533 --> 00:00:39.800
Did you just leave?

19
00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:41.133
What else can I do if I stay?

20
00:00:41.133 --> 00:00:42.966
I found an aquatic plant behind your house

21
00:00:43.166 --> 00:00:44.100
It's water hyacinth.

22
00:00:44.466 --> 00:00:46.500
Life under the white river

23
00:00:46.966 --> 00:00:48.266
If it is possible

24
00:00:48.266 --> 00:00:50.633
Please help me take care of my little son

